extends java.util.LinkedList<UdacityCourseList.Course>
implements Connection.OnConnectionReadyListener

Course List managing class. Manages the model for this application. This class updates its own state using a connection to create a local representation of the courrent account's list of courses and their units and nuggets.

addOnChangeListener

public boolean addOnChangeListener(UdacityCourseList.OnCourseListChangeListener listener)
Add a OnCourseListChangeListener to this object. Any number of listeners is acceptable, they are managed as a HashSet. Even if a listener is added more than once, it will only be notified once.

Parameters:
listener - OnCourseChangeListener to add to this object
Returns:
true if this is the first time this object has been added to this set
